      "id": 66960,
      "postNumber": 5,
      "createdAt": "2021-10-25T19:04:34.723Z",
      "author": "djbeame (Bernard Wilson)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>I have just started using this to label column headers but have found quite a few that don’t work.</p>\n<p>For example: <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/card_index_dividers.png?v=10\" title=\":card_index_dividers:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":card_index_dividers:\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/file_folder.png?v=10\" title=\":file_folder:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":file_folder:\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/hammer_and_wrench.png?v=10\" title=\":hammer_and_wrench:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":hammer_and_wrench:\" /></p>\n<p>I can put them in and then after I reload the page they are gone. Maybe I’m doing something wrong?</p>"
